Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿下 立刻拿下这座修道院 快点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Take it! Take the priory, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住 一击毙命 保留全尸\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Remember, death blows only! All limbs intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁止食尸\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't eat any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快睡吧 笨蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sleep, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我应该找副灵柩当床\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe I should get a coffin to sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没出什么事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Nothing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直以来太寂寞了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've been so alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候给你一点奖励了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's time for your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-跟我一起来吧  -好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Will you come with me? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-做我的人  -好 好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Be mine. - Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 你是我的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Tell me you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 你属于我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Tell me you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我属于你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. I belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忠诚于我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Be loyal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿忠诚于你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll be loyal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What the fuck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个黑暗生物在控制它\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The creature's controlling it!
